title: Andreea Laiu
text:
Andreea Laiu (born 15 March 1986) is a <a href="Romania">Romania</a>n <a href="women%27s%20soccer">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a> or <a href="Striker%20%28association%20football%29">striker</a> who plays for <a href="F.C.%20Kiryat%20Gat%20%28women%29">Kiryat Gat</a>. She previously played for <a href="Apollon%20Ladies%20F.C.">Apollon Limassol</a> of <a href="Cyprus">Cyprus</a>' <a href="Cypriot%20First%20Division%20%28women%29">First Division</a>.
For ten years she was a member of the <a href="Romania%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Romania national team</a>, but was not called up after 2014.
